# I have successfully collected 10 Coal, along with my existing resources of 5 Stone and 10 Iron Ore.
# Now, I can insert Coal into the Stone Furnace to fuel it for smelting.

insert_item(Prototype.Coal, furnace, quantity=5)  # Insert 5 Coal into the Stone Furnace.
print(f"Inventory after inserting fuel: {inspect_inventory()}")
